                                        <p class="font-sofia text-[17px] font-light leading-6 tracking-[-0.25px] text-charcoal whitespace-pre-wrap pt-2 uncropped">‚ÄúYesterday I was clever, so I tried to change the world. Today I am wise, so I am changing myself.‚Äù  ‚ÄîRumi
                                            üëã Hi! I‚Äôm the Founder &amp; Exec Chairman of Sift (sift.com), currently valued at $1.5B+. Sift uses realtime large-scale machine learning to help businesses prevent online fraud and reduce friction in their user journey. As CEO, I scaled us from idea to $100M ARR &amp; 400+ employees, and raised $150M+
                                            I struggled with heavy depression for a decade üò• I‚Äôve also made every mistake in the book‚Ä¶ please laugh at and learn from my pain üòâ. At minimum, I want to help you feel less alone. ‚ÄúHeavy is the head that wears the crown‚Äù. I apply loving Challenge &amp; Support to help my clients open their minds and hearts as we embark on the most important journey in life - our journey within üßòüèª I am passionate about helping people live authentic, peaceful, joyful lives.
                                            I *love* helping with:
