                                <h3 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-[21px] md:text-[18px] mt-[28px] mb-[3px]">Virtual consultation</h3>
                                <p class="font-light md:text-base md:leading-[22px] text-lg leading-[1.45] md:px-[10px]">Join the 1-on-1 video call, ask questions, and get expert advice</p>
